ich radikal Begriffs- und Denksysteme in Frage stellt, auf welche unter anderem Theorien der Kunst, der Literatur, der Kultur, der Medialität und der Gesellschaft aufbauen.  aThe issues of language constantly challenge the mind. That questions philosophical and scientific systems, changes them and keeps them moving.  afunded by Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aLanguage and languagesxPhilosophy. 4aDekonstruktion. 4aDeutsche Philosophiegeschichte. 4aDifferenz. 4aGermanistik. 4aHans-Georg Gadamer. 4aHermeneutik. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aMartin Heidegger. 4aNiklas Luhmann. 4aRoman Jakobson. 4aSemiologie. 4aSprache. 4aSprachwissenschaft. 4aSystemtheorie. 4aWilhelm Von Humboldt. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aDeconstruction.  aDifference.  aGerman History of Philosophy.  aGerman Literature.  aHans-georg Gadamer.  aHermeneutics.  aLanguage.  aLinguistics.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aMartin Heidegger.  aNiklas Luhmann.  aRoman Jakobson.  aSemiology.  aSystems Theory.  aWilhelm Von Humboldt.2 aDeutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2017z9783110548198oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839438978zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839438978423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839438978/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL 